title: The Telegraph and BT Business networking events
text: The Telegraph and BT Business networking events are designed to bring together small and medium-sized businesses and create the breeding ground for new, unexpected and successful relationships. Since each event is tailored to suit the business needs of the local area, activities and talks will range from seminars on body language to inspirational and practical discussions from successful entrepreneurs. Simply fill in the form below to register your interest. Online Form - The Telegraph and BT Business networking events
